    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I wrote a <a href="https://github.com/SonnyRajagopalan/TimerAndCallback">telecommunications stub for managing timers and a signaling stack a while ago</a>. If I wrote it now, I would probably use the clean interfaces of <a href="http://www.theron-library.com">Theron</a> (or ACT++). The biggest issue in my signaling application was the mapping of an incoming message to the right sender and struct. Will this problem be less complex in Theron?</p>
